Usually when we talk about suicide, we say those four magic words “just ask for help”. But it’s not always that simple.

It can be incredibly difficult to continue living when I feel suicidal. I didnt chooses to feel suicidal intentionally, but this feeling is a reality for many me. I may currently be in a lot of pain, but I never know what’s in store for my future.
When you feel like giving up, just remember the reason why you held on for so long.
